The paper deals with authorship attribution of natural language text, which is a common topic in computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of complex network analysis is also relevant to social network analysis (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves experiments and evaluation, which are common in information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) research.
